Title: Municipal Court Judges Clement D. Nye and Joseph Marchetti shaking hands, Los Angeles, 1934
Description.caption: Text from negative sleeve: Marchetti, Joseph Judge|~|Handwritten on negative: Judge Joseph Marchetti, Judge Clement D Nye
Description.note: Possibly related to the article,"Marchetti Sworn in As Judge," Los Angeles Times, 17 Apr. 1934: A2.|~|Los Angeles Municipal Court Judges Clement D. Nye and Joseph Marchetti shaking hands, with Judge Nye placing his other hand on Judge Marchetti's shoulder. This photograph may have been taken in Judge Nye's courtroom, where Judge Marchetti was sworn in by Justice Stephens of the Appellate Court.
